testSteps.description: Prepare approved bank profile with likeness indicator SIMILAR

children.description: Get bank accounts for EJ account 131990489 with APPROVED profiles and SIMILAR likeness indicator

reportData.title: SQL query for AMC_PROFILE
reportData.contents: SELECT bank_profile.bank_profile_guid as bank_profile_guid, bank_profile.registration_likeness_cd, bank_profile.account_id as account_id, bank_account.bank_account_guid as bank_account_guid, bank_account.bank_account_no as bank_account_no, bank_account.bank_na as bank_na, bank_account.routing_no as routing_no, bank_account.bank_account_type_cd as bank_account_type_cd, bank_account.bank_account_ownership_type_cd as bank_account_ownership_type_cd, bank_account.bank_account_nick_na as bank_account_nick_na, bank_account.bank_account_legal_entity_na as bank_account_legal_entity_na FROM bank_profile, bank_account WHERE bank_profile.bank_account_id = bank_account.bank_account_id and bank_profile.account_id = 131990489 and bank_profile.bank_profile_status_cd='APPROVED' and bank_profile.registration_likeness_cd='SIMILAR'

children.description: Get bank name by routing number 101000695

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select BK_NA
from PROD.BK_DATA_HST_11218
where
BK_RTE_NO=101000695
and END_TS is null
